 Okay. Years ago I thought of a afterlife scenario while convalescing in Ontario with family on my mom's side. I had begun an business and advertised at school. I received note that I would give products for free or ... . I put the note in my pants to contemplate the appropriate response for me, my business and my money. My mom found the note in the pants in the laundry. I was informed the police had been called and the young man talked to. That summer I was flown to a Aunt's to convalesce for the summer. 

his thought pattern
began when I was fifteen
years old.
The year was nineteen
eighty-four.
